Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBQMActivity

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBQMActivity
public class JDBQMActivity
extends java.lang.Object
The JDBQMActivity class is part of a structure within the database which represents the SAP Inspection Lot hierarchy. This is the second level. Each activity belongs to an Inspection. The data is stored in a table called APP_QM_ACTIVITY.

See Also:
JDBQMInspection, JDBQMDictionary
